{"tid":1490561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次升級，師出有名了！","createTime":"2019-08-20T06:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:54:06.000Z","uid":196536,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb1351ea2a288e8ccc5e2c16478ede87a194d33","tid":1490561,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"政府倒行逆施，無視七位數市民訴求，以致無辜市民遇襲危殆！<br />\n在暴力惡化以致市民捐軀前，香港人要設死線將行動升級！<br />\n以武制暴，刻不容緩！<br />\n設死線於31/8，夠唔夠時間醞釀？<br />\n定應該set早d? 我地要食住818個勢！<br />\n和理非100萬，200萬+1，170萬+6你唔聽，勇武回合開始！<br />\n搭配不合作運動，機場，主要幹道，地鐵！<br />\n要用今次契機破樽頸，機不可失！<br />\n同意請幫手推+討論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：以上內容純粹發夢</span>"},{"pid":"0139665c290feb2c1a8515966feb45f081f357b4","tid":1490561,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:10:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f25db22fc305653a3e8787ee98a6ade87da2c996","tid":1490561,"uid":167435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:11:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed9a7e53e6cac144e8a7dda63372edb21cbcce14","tid":1490561,"uid":3571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"715c717e86ae1c266ecc083339658fd07c176188","tid":1490561,"uid":307857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"宜家踢緊冰島對鍠馬<br />\n<br />\n只係踢到中場休息,重有下半場<br />\n<br />\n球証全部都係對面d人<br />\n<br />\n成隊有700人受傷<br />\n<br />\n互無入球<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">輸左呢場波,就會俾金仔捉去打靶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n隨時比死更難受<br />\n<br />\n冰島=兼職義士<br />\n鍠馬=職業殺手<br />\n<br />\n金仔=共產主義"},{"pid":"42a32a55089a8892a9cc58758994db076e6238ce","tid":1490561,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:14:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd7e5cb41c6f8e3b33f478be4ac1a1aead17d27e","tid":1490561,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:14